<!-- 利用系数说明弹窗 -->
<view wx:if="{{showUtilFactorModal}}" class="util-modal-mask" bindtap="closeUtilFactorModal">
  <view class="util-modal-content" catchtap="stopPropagation">
    <view class="util-modal-close" bindtap="closeUtilFactorModal">×</view>
    
    <view class="util-modal-header">
      <text class="util-modal-title">利用系数说明</text>
      <text class="util-modal-subtitle">选择层高和色彩自动估算</text>
    </view>
    
    <scroll-view scroll-y class="util-modal-body">
      <!-- 层高表格 -->
      <view class="util-section">
        <view class="util-section-title">
          <text>层高参考</text>
        </view>
        <view class="util-table">
          <view class="util-table-row header">
            <text class="util-cell col-height">层高/米</text>
            <text class="util-cell col-rate">反射率参考</text>
            <text class="util-cell col-desc">说明</text>
          </view>
          <view class="util-table-row">
            <text class="util-cell col-height">2.2-2.4</text>
            <text class="util-cell col-rate">0.90-0.95</text>
            <text class="util-cell col-desc">极低层高，光传播距离短，反射损耗极小</text>
          </view>
          <view class="util-table-row">
            <text class="util-cell col-height">2.5-2.7</text>
            <text class="util-cell col-rate">0.85-0.90</text>
            <text class="util-cell col-desc">标准住宅层高，常规反射情况良好</text>
          </view>
          <view class="util-table-row">
            <text class="util-cell col-height">2.8-3.0</text>
            <text class="util-cell col-rate">0.80-0.85</text>
            <text class="util-cell col-desc">中高层高住宅、商业空间，光稍有损耗</text>
          </view>
          <view class="util-table-row">
            <text class="util-cell col-height">3.1-3.5</text>
            <text class="util-cell col-rate">0.75-0.80</text>
            <text class="util-cell col-desc">常见餐饮、展厅、开放式商业空间</text>
          </view>
          <view class="util-table-row">
            <text class="util-cell col-height">3.6-4.0</text>
            <text class="util-cell col-rate">0.65-0.75</text>
            <text class="util-cell col-desc">高挑空空间、局部LOFT、双眼皮吊顶下隐藏灯带</text>
          </view>
          <view class="util-table-row">
            <text class="util-cell col-height">4.1-5.0</text>
            <text class="util-cell col-rate">0.50-0.65</text>
            <text class="util-cell col-desc">挑空客厅、艺术空间，需要补强照度或多层光源配合</text>
          </view>
          <view class="util-table-row">
            <text class="util-cell col-height">5.1-6.0</text>
            <text class="util-cell col-rate">0.40-0.50</text>
            <text class="util-cell col-desc">大挑空、剧场、礼堂类空间，需要专门光学设计</text>
          </view>
          <view class="util-table-row">
            <text class="util-cell col-height">6.0以上</text>
            <text class="util-cell col-rate">≤0.40</text>
            <text class="util-cell col-desc">建议结合聚光灯、下照轨道等高效配光灯具，靠间接照明几乎无效</text>
          </view>
        </view>
      </view>

      <!-- 色彩表格 -->
      <view class="util-section">
        <view class="util-section-title">
          <text>色彩参考</text>
        </view>
        <view class="util-table">
          <view class="util-table-row header">
            <text class="util-cell col-material">材质/颜色</text>
            <text class="util-cell col-rate">反射率参考</text>
            <text class="util-cell col-example">包含类型</text>
          </view>
          <view class="util-table-row">
            <text class="util-cell col-material">浅色材质</text>
            <text class="util-cell col-rate">0.7-0.85</text>
            <text class="util-cell col-example">白色、肌肤白等浅色乳胶漆墙面</text>
          </view>
          <view class="util-table-row">
            <text class="util-cell col-material">木质类材质</text>
            <text class="util-cell col-rate">0.5-0.7</text>
            <text class="util-cell col-example">原木色、木纹色家具/护墙板表面</text>
          </view>
          <view class="util-table-row">
            <text class="util-cell col-material">细腻深色材质</text>
            <text class="util-cell col-rate">0.2-0.4</text>
            <text class="util-cell col-example">黑灰色软包、金属表面</text>
          </view>
          <view class="util-table-row">
            <text class="util-cell col-material">粗糙深色材质</text>
            <text class="util-cell col-rate">0.1-0.2</text>
            <text class="util-cell col-example">水泥漆、吸光材质</text>
          </view>
        </view>
      </view>

      <view class="util-note">
        <text class="util-note-text">提示：利用系数 = 层高系数 × 色彩系数。本计算器会根据您的选择自动计算出合适的利用系数值。</text>
      </view>
    </scroll-view>
    
    <view class="util-modal-footer">
      <button class="util-btn-confirm" bindtap="closeUtilFactorModal">我知道了</button>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>

